the last part of your paper!

64
00:06:33,870 --> 00:06:37,500
Park Young Bae, those kids are dating, right?

65
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:39,790
No.

66
00:06:39,790 --> 00:06:45,930
What do you mean no?
That little girl is so lucky!

67
00:06:45,930 --> 00:06:49,640
Hey, hurry up and change your clothes.
Got it?

68
00:06:59,050 --> 00:07:03,590
Yeah. I didn't get rained on that much.

69
00:07:03,590 --> 00:07:08,420
