89
00:09:38,140 --> 00:09:43,770
Now, let's apply this right away.
Who can we have solve this problem?

90
00:09:44,950 --> 00:09:47,870
How about Hui Yeong?

91
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:56,000
- Yes.
- Why are you distracted? What's the matter today?

92
00:09:56,000 --> 00:10:02,870
Teach, it seems that Ma Hui Yeong can't concentrate
due to his girlfriend making her appearance here today.

93
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:06,350
Aigoo, it's big trouble.

94
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:10,100
That shouldn't be happening.
What should we do?

95
00:10:10,180 --> 00:10:16,270
Teach!
Instead, I, who don't have an iota of a girlfriend

96
00:10:16,270 --> 00:10:20,420
- will solve it.
- Okay. Go ahead and solve it.

97
00:10:20,420 --> 00:10:23,370
Also, why do you think you don't have a girlfriend?

98
00:10:23,370 --> 00:10:27,370
Hey, Hwang Ro Mi, Yoo Soo Bin comes to our academy.

99
00:10:28,710 --> 00:10:32,140
I'm home.

100
00:10:46,070 --> 00:10:48,930
I'm here.

101
00:10:50,830 --> 00:10:53,510
Okay.

102
00:10:53,510 --> 00:10:58,280
It went well?
You got a good lesson?

103
00:10:58,280 --> 00:11:00,310
It was okay.

104
00:11:00,310 --> 00:11:04,230
Mom, is anything the matter here?
Does it hurt?

105
00:11:04,230 --> 00:11:07,950
I got hurt while running after you.

106
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:17,710
I'm sorry. I just...
Because of the way you were with Hui Yeong's mom,

107
00:11:17,710 --> 00:11:20,090
I got a little upset.

108
00:11:20,090 --> 00:11:28,170
Soo Bin, I know, too, that I bother you incessantly.

109
00:11:28,170 --> 00:11:34,680
I know, too, that I shouldn't do that.
I try not to, but it's not working out well.

110
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:41,440
The only child I have,
my girl whom I love the most in the world.

111
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:48,380
What if you get mistreated by going to a less reputable school?

112
00:11:48,380 --> 00:11:53,710
