That's how I think.

114
00:12:01,660 --> 00:12:05,650
Mom.
Sleep comfortably.

115
00:12:05,650 --> 00:12:10,360
This is why your shoulder always gets numb.

116
00:12:12,180 --> 00:12:17,370
I'll study hard.
Don't worry so much.

117
00:12:28,650 --> 00:12:31,400
That was worth me getting hurt.

118
