132
00:16:35,330 --> 00:16:37,520
- Oh, you're washing?
- My eyes are stinging. Hurry.

133
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:41,160
- Yeah, Joon Woo. Make sure you eat breakfast and--
- Yeah, breakfast. Uh-huh.

134
00:16:41,160 --> 00:16:44,780
- And make sure you dress tidy, and the handkerchief--
- Yeah, the handkerchief? Okay.

135
00:16:44,780 --> 00:16:49,510
