00:17:42,910 --> 00:17:47,740
Joon Woo.
Choi Joon Woo, come here.

141
00:17:47,740 --> 00:17:51,280
Choi... Hey!

142
00:18:05,970 --> 00:18:10,750
You didn't know the requirements, did you?
What's with your mask?

143
00:18:13,420 --> 00:18:17,900
Wow, you're a good actor.
It's not like you're an idol or something. Come here.

144
00:18:17,900 --> 00:18:20,920
Stand still. Take it off.

145
00:18:20,920 --> 00:18:24,010
