146
00:18:24,010 --> 00:18:26,930
- Hi, Teacher Oh! Good morning.
- Yeah, good morning.

147
00:18:26,930 --> 00:18:31,540
- It's hot, and he caught a cold, so...
- I see.

148
00:18:31,540 --> 00:18:34,210
Work hard.

149
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:41,390
Hey, what's wrong with you? Did you fight?
Where, when, and whom with?

150
00:18:41,390 --> 00:18:44,090
No. While riding the bike.

151
00:18:44,090 --> 00:18:48,510
You got hurt this specifically while riding a bike?
I see.

152
00:18:48,510 --> 00:18:50,800
You don't want to talk, huh?

153
00:18:52,360 --> 00:18:58,770
Fine. Fine. No report came through to the school, so I don't think it was something big. There's nothing special going on?

154
00:18:58,770 --> 00:19:01,970
No. I'm sorry.

155
00:19:01,970 --> 00:19:06,710
