174
00:20:50,860 --> 00:20:53,180
A little.

175
00:21:01,230 --> 00:21:04,210
A little probably won't do.

176
00:21:15,010 --> 00:21:18,900
I washed it. Thank you.

177
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:26,130
Oh. If you...
do that, it'll get wrinkled.

178
00:21:26,130 --> 00:21:29,570
I ironed it well for you.

179
00:21:51,910 --> 00:21:56,890
You said you didn't have an iron,
but it looks well pressed.

180
00:22:06,860 --> 00:22:10,260
Ro Mi, I scribbled down a few things for our EF, and—

181
00:22:10,260 --> 00:22:12,020
Yoon Pil Sang.

182
00:22:12,020 --> 00:22:13,750
Get lost.

183
00:22:13,770 --> 00:22:16,050
Okay. Right.

184
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:26,930
- Hi, hi.
- Hi!

185
00:22:26,930 --> 00:22:29,310
- Hi.
- What are you doing?

186
00:22:29,320 --> 00:22:31,090
Smells.

187
00:22:39,310 --> 00:22:41,990
Joon Woo, did you get into something?

188
00:22:41,990 --> 00:22:44,370
Fight?

189
00:22:46,560 --> 00:22:49,950
Oh, Choi Joon Woo,
I guess you got into a fight yesterday.

190
00:22:49,950 --> 00:22:53,630
Who was it?
Our area has been quiet these days...

191
00:22:53,670 --> 00:22:56,650
Right, Pil Sang?
Pil Sang.

192
00:22:56,650 --> 00:22:59,500
Hey, Choi Joon Woo must have gotten beat up somewhere.

193
00:22:59,500 --> 00:23:02,240
- Right? That's why he's wearing a mask, right?
- Yeah.

194
00:23:02,240 --> 00:23:04,520
As expected, that FT (forced transfer) kid.

195
00:23:04,520 --> 00:23:08,580
I don't think so.
I heard that he fell off his bike.

196
00:23:08,580 --> 00:23:11,990
- What.
- No, no. I doubt it.

197
00:23:13,280 --> 00:23:14,860
Yoo Soo Bin.

198
00:23:14,860 --> 00:23:16,430
Yes, Ro Mi?

199
00:23:16,500 --> 00:23:19,200
- I heard you're taking Teacher Son's class.
- Really?

200
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:22,400
Oh, did you pass the level test?
I knew you could do it.

201
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:26,500
I heard it's not easy to even take the level test.
How did you take it?

202
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:30,380
- What happened is...
- I recommended her.

203
00:23:30,380 --> 00:23:32,620
Because I thought she was qualified.

204
00:23:32,620 --> 00:23:36,200
Did you even take the level test?

205
00:23:36,200 --> 00:23:38,910
Yes. Ro Mi, can you come talk to me for a second--

206
00:23:38,910 --> 00:23:42,360
Hwi Yeong, let's talk.

207
00:23:44,100 --> 00:23:47,720
Later. I need to do this now.

208
00:23:51,500 --> 00:23:53,000
Later.

209
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:55,300
No, let's talk right now.

210
00:23:55,310 --> 00:23:57,110
Hey, Hwang Ro Mi.

211
00:23:57,110 --> 00:23:59,770
- That rude brat.
- Stop it.

