213
00:24:01,760 --> 00:24:03,080
- Ro Mi.
- Now, now.

214
00:24:03,080 --> 00:24:06,960
Let's get started. Take your seats.

215
00:24:09,940 --> 00:24:14,030
Why does the mood seem so dark?

216
00:24:15,130 --> 00:24:18,280
