so I didn't feel the need to tell you.

225
00:24:56,310 --> 00:25:00,200
But you passed, thanks to Hwi Yeong's favor.

226
00:25:01,520 --> 00:25:04,180
I did pass.

227
00:25:04,180 --> 00:25:08,930
I think that I passed because of my own skills.
When I got home, I went over the problems.

228
00:25:08,930 --> 00:25:11,600
And I did pretty well on the test.

229
00:25:11,600 --> 00:25:15,540
So annoying.
This type of special treatment and opportunities.

230
00:25:15,560 --> 00:25:17,700
- Ro Mi, It's not like that.
- Stop.

231
00:25:17,700 --> 00:25:20,410
I don't want to talk to you.

232
00:25:20,410 --> 00:25:22,240
Hwang Ro Mi.

233
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:32,430
Did you two fight?

234
00:25:33,540 --> 00:25:35,750
I'm not you.

235
00:25:37,910 --> 00:25:40,870
Yes, we fought.

236
00:25:41,740 --> 00:25:43,960
Did you win?

237
00:25:46,580 --> 00:25:49,070
Then you did win.

