01:04:18,290 --> 01:04:21,700
♬ Everything fades away ♬

765
01:04:21,700 --> 01:04:25,030
♬ Let it go by with a flow ♬

766
01:04:25,030 --> 01:04:28,400
♬ Never quite understood it ♬

767
01:04:28,400 --> 01:04:30,000
♬ when you told me ♬

768
01:04:30,000 --> 01:04:32,950
Moment at Eighteen
~ Preview ~

769
01:04:32,970 --> 01:04:34,840
Did you give money to those guys?
Are you crazy?

770
01:04:34,840 --> 01:04:36,570
Do you think he's going to be loyal to you?

771
01:04:36,570 --> 01:04:38,430
My friend died because of you guys.

772
01:04:38,430 --> 01:04:39,830
I'll even get on my knees.

773
01:04:39,830 --> 01:04:41,910
You're already a goner, but I'm not, Joon Woo.

774
01:04:41,910 --> 01:04:44,560
When Choi Joon Woo was beating you,
why did you just take it?

775
01:04:44,610 --> 01:04:46,220
I guess I was like that in front of Ma Hui Yeong?

776
01:04:46,220 --> 01:04:47,910
If you feel wronged, I wanted to help.

777
01:04:47,910 --> 01:04:50,960
Why would you help me?
Is it pity?

778
01:04:51,000 --> 01:04:53,730
Could you please tell me exactly what you saw?

779
01:04:53,730 --> 01:04:54,570
Thank you, Geon Hyeok.

780
01:04:54,570 --> 01:04:56,350
Mom, help me.

781
01:04:56,350 --> 01:04:57,180
Embarrassed?
You’re embarrassed?!

782
01:04:57,180 --> 01:04:59,840
Did you give birth to me because you
wanted to brag and show off?

783
01:04:59,840 --> 01:05:01,430
I can't go to Seoul University.

784
01:05:01,430 --> 01:05:02,160
Are you okay?

785
01:05:02,200 --> 01:05:05,000
Why am I doing this to you?
You're asking if it's out of pity?

786
01:05:05,000 --> 01:05:07,850
♬ Oh you know me ♬

787
01:05:08,430 --> 01:05:12,630
♬ All the moments we shared
are not going anywhere ♬
